              <p class="subheading understanding center space margin">COOPERACY PLATFORM WHITE PAPER</p>
              <p class="base">This white paper explains how the Cooperacy platform works in detail.</p>
              <p class="subheading understanding center space margin">THE FUNDING ECOSYSTEM</p>
              <p class="base">Cooperacy <i>collection fund</i> is an amount of money generated by every member's one euro monthly subscription. One euro per month is 0.00000039 euros or 0.39 micro-euro per second:</p>

